const description =
	"Scrum Product Owners need to embrace and actively pursue continuous learning and skill development. The best courses for Product Owners are ones that equip them with the knowledge and expertise needed to communicate effectively to deliver products to delight customers. In addition to Certified Scrum Product Owner training, there are various other topics that can further ..."
